title: Opie & Jim Norton JUN 11 2015 Thu.mp3
description:
THANKS TO @SternGeek FOR THE FILE


We start the show recapping our interview with Chyna and X-Pac from yesterday, Iliza Shlesinger joins the show, we talk to Iliza about her appearance on The View yesterday, we talk about clothing and footwear and what to call panties, we watch clips of Iliza on The View, and we discuss comas. 

We talk about Jerry Seinfeld and his comments on PC college kids, we discuss the latest on the prison escape, and we watch an eye witness with green hair being interviewed. 

Ann Coulter stops by to discuss her new book on immigration, and Colin Quinn joins the show to talk about his new book
